Write a C Program to check a number is even or odd using functions with return

#include <stdio.h>
int checkeven_or_odd(int x);
int main()
{
  int x,ans;
  printf("Enter a number:");
  scanf("%d",&x);
  ans=checkeven_or_odd(x);
  if(ans==0)
  printf("Even");
  else
  printf("Odd");
}

int checkeven_or_odd(int x)
{
    if(x%2==0)
    return 0;
    else
    return 1;
}

INPUT AND OUTPUT:

INPUT:
Enter a number: 6

OUTPUT:
Even
